<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: 2cm 2.5cm; }
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.7; }
    h1 { font-size: 14pt; text-align: center; color: #1e3a5f; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; color: #555; font-size: 9pt; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 12px 0 20px 0; }
    .section-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; color: #1e3a5f; text-decoration: underline; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .info-table td { vertical-align: top; padding: 3px 4px; font-size: 10pt; }
    .info-table td.lbl { width: 200px; color: #555; }
    .info-table td.val { font-weight: bold; }
    .amount-box { background: #f0f4f8; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding: 10px 14px; margin: 14px 0; }
    .amount-label { font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .amount-value { font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; }
    .amount-detail { font-size: 9pt; color: #555; margin-top: 4px; }
    .sign-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 36px; }
    .sign-table td { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 12px; vertical-align: top; }
    .sign-label { font-size: 9pt; font-weight: bold; color: #444; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .sign-space { height: 60px; }
    .legal { font-size: 8pt; color: #888; margin-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 8px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Attestation de loyer</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">À destination de la Caisse d'Allocations Familiales (CAF)</p>
  <hr>

  <p>Je soussigné(e), <strong>{{ bailleur_name }}</strong>, bailleur du logement désigné ci-dessous,
  atteste sur l'honneur que les informations ci-après sont exactes :</p>

  <div class="section-title">1. Le logement</div>
  <table class="info-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Adresse :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ property_address }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Référence / type de logement :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ unit_ref }} — {{ unit_type }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% if area_sqm %}
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Surface habitable :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ area_sqm }} m²</td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
  </table>

  <div class="section-title">2. Le locataire</div>
  <table class="info-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Nom et prénom :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ tenant_name }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% if tenant_birth_date %}
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Date de naissance :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ tenant_birth_date }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
  </table>

  <div class="section-title">3. Le contrat de location</div>
  <table class="info-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Date de prise d'effet :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ start_date }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Type de bail :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ lease_type_label }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl">Statut du bail :</td>
      <td class="val">{{ 'Bail en cours' if is_active else 'Bail résilié' }}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="section-title">4. Montant du loyer</div>
  <div class="amount-box">
    <div class="amount-label">Loyer mensuel total charges comprises (TCC)</div>
    <div class="amount-value">{{ total_monthly }} €</div>
    <div class="amount-detail">
      Loyer hors charges : {{ rent_amount }} €
      &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;
      Charges locatives : {{ charges_amount }} €
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>Fait à {% if property_city %}{{ property_city }}{% else %}________________________{% endif %}, le {{ today }}</p>

  <table class="sign-table">
    <tr>
      <td style="width: 50%;">
        <div class="sign-label">Signature du bailleur</div>
        <div style="font-size: 9pt; color: #555; margin-bottom: 8px;">{{ bailleur_name }}</div>
        <div class="sign-space"></div>
      </td>
      <td style="width: 50%;">
        <div class="sign-label">Cachet / Tampon (facultatif)</div>
        <div class="sign-space"></div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="legal">
    Document généré par LeComptoirImmo &bull;
    Cette attestation est établie à la demande du locataire pour faire valoir ce que de droit.
    Le bailleur certifie l'exactitude des informations déclarées.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
